reviewText: I am a fan, so had to have this.  Blue Ray works on US devices.  Don't buy a DVD unless correct region.  Excellent document of their Hiroshima concert.
excellent concert! came quickly, good quality - no issues

Great picture and sound quality. Loved the concert. I do have to say its on the expensive side, but definitely worth the money. The tracklist for the concert was excellent, the only thing I might wish was added was special features and menu options. Looking forward to the World Tour 3rd dvd!
